  "prompt": "If I don't clear the ASAT, will I not be able to get into the ALLEN Career Institute?",
  "response": "If you don't clear the ASAT (ALLEN Scholarship Cum Admission Test), it may affect your ability to get into the ALLEN Career Institute, as the ASAT is a key part of their admission process. However, admission policies can vary and there might be other pathways or subsequent opportunities to apply. It's best to contact ALLEN Career Institute directly to inquire about alternative admission options or future test dates if you're unable to clear the ASAT on your first attempt.",
